---
layout: basic/content.hbs
preheader: "Use this link to reset your password. The link is only valid for 24 hours."
---
<h1>Hi ${f:escapeHtml(user.firstName)},</h1>
<p>You recently requested to reset your password for your {{product_name}} account. Use the button below to reset it. <strong>This password reset is only valid for the next ${f:formatTimeDiffDateNowInUserLocale(resetPasswordTokenExpirationDate)}.</strong></p>

<!-- Action -->
<table class="body-action" align="center" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      {{> button label="Reset your password" target_url="{{resetPasswordLink}}?fromURI=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.variance.com" }}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or <a href="https://www.variance.com/contact">contact support</a> if you have questions.</p>
<p>Thanks,<br>The {{product_name}} Team</p>

{{> button_trouble var="{{resetPasswordLink}}?fromURI=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.variance.com" }}
